# Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy

Last updated: July 21, 2026

CFA Level I Learner ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use our mobile application.

1. Information We Collect

This application operates entirely offline and does NOT collect, store, or transmit any personal information. We do not require account creation, login, or any form of registration.

2. Local Storage Only

All data generated while using this app (including study progress, quiz scores, notes, bookmarks, and language preferences) is stored exclusively on your device using local storage mechanisms (LocalForage). No data is transmitted to any external server or third party.

3. No Third-Party Services

This application does not integrate any third-party analytics, advertising, tracking, or crash reporting services. The app functions fully offline with no network communication.

4. No Data Collection

We do not collect, use, or share any personal data, usage statistics, device information, or location data. There is no analytics SDK, tracking code, or telemetry of any kind embedded in this application.

5. Children's Privacy

Our application is designed for adult learners preparing for financial examinations. We do not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 13.

6. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the application and on this page. Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

7. Third-Party Links

The application may contain references to external resources (such as CFA Institute). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties.

8. Disclaimer

This application is an unofficial study aid and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or approved by CFA Institute. CFA Institute does not endorse or promote this application.

9. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact the developer at the email address listed on the Google Play Store listing or Email: ivanng611@gmail.com

10. Complete Offline Operation

This app is designed to work 100% offline. No internet connection is required after installation. We deliberately chose not to implement any network features to ensure your complete privacy.
